{
  "uid": "ai-obs-loadgen",
  "title": "AI o11y — Loadgen Activity (what k6 is driving right now)",
  "tags": [
    "ai-observability",
    "loadgen",
    "k6",
    "operations"
  ],
  "timezone": "",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 1,
  "refresh": "30s",
  "time": {
    "from": "now-30m",
    "to": "now"
  },
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "current": {
          "selected": false,
          "text": "default",
          "value": "default"
        },
        "hide": 0,
        "includeAll": false,
        "label": "Prometheus",
        "multi": false,
        "name": "datasource_prom",
        "options": [],
        "query": "prometheus",
        "refresh": 1,
        "regex": "",
        "skipUrlSync": false,
        "type": "datasource"
      },
      {
        "current": {
          "selected": false,
          "text": "default",
          "value": "default"
        },
        "hide": 0,
        "includeAll": false,
        "label": "Loki",
        "multi": false,
        "name": "datasource_loki",
        "options": [],
        "query": "loki",
        "refresh": 1,
        "regex": "",
        "skipUrlSync": false,
        "type": "datasource"
      }
    ]
  },
  "annotations": {
    "list": []
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Loadgen activity — overview",
      "gridPos": {"h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0},
      "collapsed": false,
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Loadgen requests / sec (5m)",
      "description": "Rate of LLM gateway sigil-generation log lines (one per chat). Proxy for live k6 throughput.",
      "gridPos": {"h": 5, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 1},
      "datasource": {"type": "loki", "uid": "${datasource_loki}"},
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": {"type": "loki", "uid": "${datasource_loki}"},
          "expr": "sum(rate({namespace=\"observibelity\",container=\"llm-gateway\"} |~ \"sigil generation\" [5m]))",
          "queryType": "instant"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false},
        "orientation": "auto",
        "textMode": "auto",
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "reqps",
          "decimals": 2,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {"color": "red", "value": null},
              {"color": "yellow", "value": 0.1},
              {"color": "green", "value": 0.5}
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Active use cases (5m)",
      "description": "Count of distinct ai_o11y.usecase values seen in LLM gateway logs.",
      "gridPos": {"h": 5, "w": 6, "x": 6, "y": 1},
      "datasource": {"type": "loki", "uid": "${datasource_loki}"},
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": {"type": "loki", "uid": "${datasource_loki}"},
          "expr": "count(sum by (ai_o11y_usecase) (count_over_time({namespace=\"observibelity\",container=\"llm-gateway\"} |~ \"ai_o11y\" | pattern `<_>\\\"ai_o11y.usecase\\\": \\\"<ai_o11y_usecase>\\\"<_>` | ai_o11y_usecase!=\"\" [5m])))",
          "queryType": "instant"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false},
        "orientation": "auto",
        "textMode": "auto",
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "decimals": 0,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {"color": "red", "value": null},
              {"color": "orange", "value": 5},
              {"color": "yellow", "value": 10},
              {"color": "green", "value": 18}
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Active personas (5m)",
      "description": "Count of distinct ai_o11y.persona_id values seen in LLM gateway logs.",
      "gridPos": {"h": 5, "w": 6, "x": 12, "y": 1},
      "datasource": {"type": "loki", "uid": "${datasource_loki}"},
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": {"type": "loki", "uid": "${datasource_loki}"},
          "expr": "count(sum by (ai_o11y_persona_id) (count_over_time({namespace=\"observibelity\",container=\"llm-gateway\"} |~ \"ai_o11y\" | pattern `<_>\\\"ai_o11y.persona_id\\\": \\\"<ai_o11y_persona_id>\\\"<_>` | ai_o11y_persona_id!=\"\" [5m])))",
          "queryType": "instant"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false},
        "orientation": "auto",
        "textMode": "auto",
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "decimals": 0,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {"color": "red", "value": null},
              {"color": "orange", "value": 5},
              {"color": "yellow", "value": 12},
              {"color": "green", "value": 20}
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "k6 spend rate (5m)",
      "description": "Live USD/hr being burned on Claude calls from k6.",
      "gridPos": {"h": 5, "w": 6, "x": 18, "y": 1},
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource_prom}"},
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource_prom}"},
          "expr": "sum(rate(gen_ai_client_cost_USD_total[5m])) * 3600",
          "queryType": "instant"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false},
        "orientation": "auto",
        "textMode": "auto",
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "currencyUSD",
          "decimals": 3,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {"color": "green", "value": null},
              {"color": "yellow", "value": 5},
              {"color": "red", "value": 25}
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Per-use-case + per-persona traffic (last 5m)",
      "gridPos": {"h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 6},
      "collapsed": false,
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "type": "barchart",
      "title": "Loadgen rate by use case (5m)",
      "description": "Total chats per use case in the last 5m. Reflects baseline.js weights * traffic rate.",
      "gridPos": {"h": 11, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 7},
      "datasource": {"type": "loki", "uid": "${datasource_loki}"},
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": {"type": "loki", "uid": "${datasource_loki}"},
          "expr": "topk(22, sum by (ai_o11y_usecase) (count_over_time({namespace=\"observibelity\",container=\"llm-gateway\"} |~ \"ai_o11y\" | pattern `<_>\\\"ai_o11y.usecase\\\": \\\"<ai_o11y_usecase>\\\"<_>` | ai_o11y_usecase!=\"\" [5m])))",
          "queryType": "instant",
          "legendFormat": "{{ai_o11y_usecase}}"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "orientation": "horizontal",
        "xTickLabelRotation": 0,
        "xTickLabelSpacing": 0,
        "showValue": "auto",
        "stacking": "none",
        "groupWidth": 0.7,
        "barWidth": 0.97,
        "barRadius": 0,
        "fullHighlight": false,
        "legend": {"showLegend": false, "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom", "calcs": []},
        "tooltip": {"mode": "single", "sort": "none"}
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "color": {"mode": "palette-classic"},
          "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [{"color": "green", "value": null}]}
        },
        "overrides": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "type": "barchart",
      "title": "Loadgen rate by persona (5m)",
      "description": "Total chats per persona in the last 5m. Centerpiece personas (Tim/Mara/Jordan/Priya/Eric) should dominate.",
      "gridPos": {"h": 11, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 7},
      "datasource": {"type": "loki", "uid": "${datasource_loki}"},
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": {"type": "loki", "uid": "${datasource_loki}"},
          "expr": "topk(25, sum by (ai_o11y_persona_id) (count_over_time({namespace=\"observibelity\",container=\"llm-gateway\"} |~ \"ai_o11y\" | pattern `<_>\\\"ai_o11y.persona_id\\\": \\\"<ai_o11y_persona_id>\\\"<_>` | ai_o11y_persona_id!=\"\" [5m])))",
          "queryType": "instant",
          "legendFormat": "{{ai_o11y_persona_id}}"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "orientation": "horizontal",
        "xTickLabelRotation": 0,
        "xTickLabelSpacing": 0,
        "showValue": "auto",
        "stacking": "none",
        "groupWidth": 0.7,
        "barWidth": 0.97,
        "barRadius": 0,
        "fullHighlight": false,
        "legend": {"showLegend": false, "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom", "calcs": []},
        "tooltip": {"mode": "single", "sort": "none"}
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "color": {"mode": "palette-classic"},
          "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [{"color": "green", "value": null}]}
        },
        "overrides": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Time series + specialists",
      "gridPos": {"h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 18},
      "collapsed": false,
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Use-case traffic over time (top 12)",
      "description": "Watch which use cases ramp / dip / die out as you tweak baseline.js.",
      "gridPos": {"h": 11, "w": 16, "x": 0, "y": 19},
      "datasource": {"type": "loki", "uid": "${datasource_loki}"},
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": {"type": "loki", "uid": "${datasource_loki}"},
          "expr": "topk(12, sum by (ai_o11y_usecase) (rate({namespace=\"observibelity\",container=\"llm-gateway\"} |~ \"ai_o11y\" | pattern `<_>\\\"ai_o11y.usecase\\\": \\\"<ai_o11y_usecase>\\\"<_>` | ai_o11y_usecase!=\"\" [5m])))",
          "queryType": "range",
          "legendFormat": "{{ai_o11y_usecase}}"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "tooltip": {"mode": "multi", "sort": "desc"},
        "legend": {"showLegend": true, "displayMode": "table", "placement": "right", "calcs": ["mean", "lastNotNull"]}
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "reqps",
          "color": {"mode": "palette-classic"},
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineInterpolation": "smooth",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "showPoints": "never",
            "spanNulls": true,
            "stacking": {"mode": "none", "group": "A"}
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "type": "piechart",
      "title": "Specialist mix (5m)",
      "description": "Which downstream specialists are being hit. Sanity-check that sb-router is fanning out correctly.",
      "gridPos": {"h": 11, "w": 8, "x": 16, "y": 19},
      "datasource": {"type": "loki", "uid": "${datasource_loki}"},
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": {"type": "loki", "uid": "${datasource_loki}"},
          "expr": "topk(15, sum by (ai_o11y_specialist) (count_over_time({namespace=\"observibelity\",container=\"llm-gateway\"} |~ \"ai_o11y\" | pattern `<_>\\\"ai_o11y.specialist\\\": \\\"<ai_o11y_specialist>\\\"<_>` | ai_o11y_specialist!=\"\" [5m])))",
          "queryType": "instant",
          "legendFormat": "{{ai_o11y_specialist}}"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {"values": false, "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": ""},
        "pieType": "donut",
        "tooltip": {"mode": "single", "sort": "desc"},
        "legend": {"showLegend": true, "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom", "values": []},
        "displayLabels": ["percent"]
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "color": {"mode": "palette-classic"}
        },
        "overrides": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Model routing + freshness",
      "gridPos": {"h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 30},
      "collapsed": false,
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "type": "piechart",
      "title": "Provider mix (5m) — should be ~90/10 Ollama/Claude",
      "description": "Configured by CLAUDE_FRACTION in baseline.js (default 0.10).",
      "gridPos": {"h": 9, "w": 8, "x": 0, "y": 31},
      "datasource": {"type": "loki", "uid": "${datasource_loki}"},
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": {"type": "loki", "uid": "${datasource_loki}"},
          "expr": "sum by (gen_ai_system) (count_over_time({namespace=\"observibelity\",container=\"llm-gateway\"} |~ \"sigil generation\" | pattern `<_>\\\"gen_ai.system\\\": \\\"<gen_ai_system>\\\"<_>` | gen_ai_system!=\"\" [5m]))",
          "queryType": "instant",
          "legendFormat": "{{gen_ai_system}}"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {"values": false, "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": ""},
        "pieType": "donut",
        "tooltip": {"mode": "single", "sort": "desc"},
        "legend": {"showLegend": true, "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom", "values": ["value", "percent"]},
        "displayLabels": ["percent"]
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "color": {"mode": "palette-classic"}
        },
        "overrides": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "type": "table",
      "title": "Use-case freshness — time since last hit",
      "description": "If a use case has gone cold (red), check baseline.js weight, k6 pod health, or routing keywords in sb-router.",
      "gridPos": {"h": 9, "w": 16, "x": 8, "y": 31},
      "datasource": {"type": "loki", "uid": "${datasource_loki}"},
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": {"type": "loki", "uid": "${datasource_loki}"},
          "expr": "topk(25, sum by (ai_o11y_usecase) (count_over_time({namespace=\"observibelity\",container=\"llm-gateway\"} |~ \"ai_o11y\" | pattern `<_>\\\"ai_o11y.usecase\\\": \\\"<ai_o11y_usecase>\\\"<_>` | ai_o11y_usecase!=\"\" [30m])))",
          "queryType": "instant",
          "legendFormat": "{{ai_o11y_usecase}}",
          "instant": true
        }
      ],
      "transformations": [
        {
          "id": "labelsToFields",
          "options": {"mode": "columns"}
        },
        {
          "id": "organize",
          "options": {
            "excludeByName": {"Time": true},
            "renameByName": {"Value": "Hits (30m)", "ai_o11y_usecase": "Use case"}
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "sortBy",
          "options": {"fields": {}, "sort": [{"field": "Hits (30m)", "desc": true}]}
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "showHeader": true,
        "cellHeight": "sm",
        "footer": {"show": false, "reducer": ["sum"], "countRows": false, "fields": ""}
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "custom": {
            "align": "auto",
            "cellOptions": {"type": "auto"},
            "inspect": false
          }
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "Hits (30m)"},
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "custom.cellOptions",
                "value": {"type": "color-background", "mode": "gradient"}
              },
              {
                "id": "thresholds",
                "value": {
                  "mode": "absolute",
                  "steps": [
                    {"color": "red", "value": null},
                    {"color": "orange", "value": 1},
                    {"color": "yellow", "value": 10},
                    {"color": "green", "value": 30}
                  ]
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Scenario config snapshot (from baseline.js)",
      "gridPos": {"h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 40},
      "collapsed": false,
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "gridPos": {"h": 22, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 41},
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## Current loadgen mix (from `baseline.js`)\n\nTop 20 weighted scenarios — the offender archetypes (Tim/Mara/Jordan/Priya/Eric) are intentionally heavy so the centerpiece panels stay lit.\n\n| Weight | Use case | Persona | App |\n|---:|---|---|---|\n| **8** | data-theft-tim | u-tim-l | supportbot |\n| **5** | hiring-discrimination-risk | u-hr-recruiter | supportbot |\n| 4 | prompt-injection | u-eric-bad | supportbot |\n| 4 | prompt-injection-llm01 | u-eric-bad | supportbot |\n| 4 | normal-support (HR) | u-emp-norm-1 | supportbot |\n| 4 | normal-support (IT) | u-emp-norm-2 | supportbot |\n| 4 | normal-shopping | u-bob-sales | neoncart |\n| 4 | normal-shopping | u-alice-eng | neoncart |\n| 4 | **mice-rca** (centerpiece) | u-customer-mice | neoncart |\n| 4 | **email-cascade** | u-mara-chen | supportbot |\n| 4 | **cost-anomaly-per-user** | u-priya-research | supportbot |\n| 4 | **confidential-disclosure** | u-jordan-finance | supportbot |\n| 3 | sensitive-data-leaks | u-emp-test-pii | supportbot |\n| 3 | refund-policy-compliance | u-shopper-refund | neoncart |\n| 3 | prompt-injection | u-shopper-injector | neoncart |\n| 3 | normal-support (hiring) | u-hr-recruiter | supportbot |\n| 3 | normal-support (expense) | u-emp-norm-3 | supportbot |\n| 3 | normal-shopping | u-carol-mktg | neoncart |\n| 3 | model-winner | u-shopper-gift | neoncart |\n| 3 | customer-frustration | u-frustrated | neoncart |\n| 3 | cost-anomaly-per-user | u-priya-research | neoncart |\n| 3 | brand-voice-drift | u-norm-2 | neoncart |\n| 3 | bad-question-askers | u-emp-rude | supportbot |\n\n...plus 16 more @ weight 2 (token-spikes, toxicity, pii-echo, tool-call-runaway, policy-circumvention, outlier-users, quality-trend, hallucination-product-price, and 8 normal-support buckets).\n\n**Total scenarios:** 47 across 22 use cases and 30 personas.\n\n## Model routing\n\n- **90%** of chats: Ollama (default `llama3.2:1b`, chart-supplied)\n- **10%** of chats: Claude — uniformly across `claude-haiku-4-5-20251001`, `claude-sonnet-4-6`, `claude-opus-4-7`\n- Controlled by `LOADGEN_CLAUDE_FRACTION` env (default `0.10`)\n- Claude pricing halved from list for demo cost-comparison\n\n## To tune the mix\n\nEdit [`/workspace/observibelity/registry/_generated/scenarios/baseline.js`](https://github.com/stephenwagner-grafana/observibelity/blob/main/registry/_generated/scenarios/baseline.js), then:\n\n```bash\nhelm upgrade observibelity /workspace/observibelity \\\n  -f /workspace/observibelity/values-deploy.yaml \\\n  --namespace observibelity --reuse-values --timeout 5m\nkubectl rollout restart -n observibelity deployment/k6-traffic\n```\n\n## Related dashboards\n\n- [Cost & spend](/d/ai-obs-cost) — total $/hr by provider / model / user\n- [NeonCart app](/d/ai-obs-app-neoncart) — per-use-case panels for nc-* scenarios\n- [SupportBot app](/d/ai-obs-app-supportbot) — per-use-case panels for sb-* scenarios\n- [Demo landing](/d/ai-obs-landing) — full demo agenda\n"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {}, "overrides": []}
    }
  ]
}
